So previously, I said three, now I'm just using the default value of five, right? So this is basically create a RAC pipeline, end to end RAC pipeline. Again, this is going to be using Plaid because it's using the Regatui package at the backend, but if you want to use PHYs as a DB or index, you can use that as well. It just needs to pass on this specific flag. Now this does the document chunking a little different, and that's why, we will get a different number of, embedding vector or dimensions.
